OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776687067
OL,3,CAmy Winehouse's father loses High
OL,4,CCourt row with singer's friends over
OL,5,Cauctions
OL,7,FAmy Winehouse's father has lost a High
OL,8,FCourt claim against two of his
OL,9,Fdaughter's friends over the auctioning
OL,10,Fof items that had been owned by the
OL,11,Fsinger.
OL,13,FMitch Winehouse, acting as the
OL,14,Fadministrator of his daughter's
OL,15,Festate, sued her stylist Naomi Parry
OL,16,Fand friend Catriona Gourlay over
OL,17,Fclaims they profited from selling
OL,18,Fdozens of items at auctions in the
OL,19,FUnited States in 2021 and 2023.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776687067
OL,3,CAmy Winehouse's father loses High
OL,4,CCourt row with singer's friends over
OL,5,Cauctions
OL,7,FLawyers for Mr Winehouse told a trial
OL,8,Fin December the two women had
OL,9,F"deliberately concealed" that they
OL,10,Fwere selling the items, and the legal
OL,11,Fproceedings were his "only means of
OL,12,Fobtaining answers".
OL,14,FMs Parry and Ms Gourlay defended the
OL,15,Fclaim, with their barristers stating
OL,16,Fthat the items were either gifted by
OL,17,FMs Winehouse or were already owned by
OL,18,Fthem.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@XO]sD@VOUtD@RO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776687067
OL,3,CAmy Winehouse's father loses High
OL,4,CCourt row with singer's friends over
OL,5,Cauctions
OL,7,FDeputy High Court judge Sarah Clarke
OL,8,FKC said in a judgment on Monday: "I
OL,9,Ffind that neither Ms Parry nor Ms
OL,10,FGourlay deliberately concealed any of
OL,11,Ftheir disputed items from the claimant
OL,12,Fand even if I am wrong about that, Mr
OL,13,FWinehouse could have discovered what
OL,14,Fdisputed items the defendants had with
OL,15,Freasonable diligence."
OL,17,FMs Winehouse, whose 2006 album Back To
OL,18,FBlack made her an international star,
OL,19,Fdied from alcohol poisoning in 2011,
OL,20,Faged 27.
OL,26,@pD@bOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776687067
OL,3,CAmy Winehouse's father loses High
OL,4,CCourt row with singer's friends over
OL,5,Cauctions
OL,7,FDuring the trial, lawyers for Ms Parry
OL,8,Faccused Mr Winehouse of bringing the
OL,9,Fclaim out of "petty jealousy", which
OL,10,Fhe denied.
OL,12,FHe said he thought the money from the
OL,13,F2021 auction would be split between
OL,14,Fhimself, Ms Winehouse's mother, Janis,
OL,15,Fand the Amy Winehouse Foundation (AWF).
OL,26,@qD@NOUqD@]O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776687067
OL,3,CAmy Winehouse's father loses High
OL,4,CCourt row with singer's friends over
OL,5,Cauctions
OL,7,FThe court heard how the auction
OL,8,Fcatalogue contained 834 items and that
OL,9,Fthe sale raised 1.4 million US dollars
OL,10,F(#1.05 million) for the Amy Winehouse
OL,11,Festate, 30% of which went to the
OL,12,Ffoundation.
OL,14,FOne item sold by Ms Parry included a
OL,15,Fsilk mini-dress worn by Ms Winehouse
OL,16,Fduring her final performance in
OL,17,FBelgrade, Serbia, which was auctioned
OL,18,Ffor 243,200 dollars (#182,656).
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776687067
OL,3,CAmy Winehouse's father loses High
OL,4,CCourt row with singer's friends over
OL,5,Cauctions
OL,7,FShe told the court that Mr Winehouse
OL,8,Fhad offered her 250,000 dollars
OL,9,F(#187,000) for the proceeds of her
OL,10,Fsale and to make the legal claim go
OL,11,Faway, but that she would "rather set
OL,12,Fthe money on fire than give him a
OL,13,Fpenny".
OL,15,FJudge Clarke said: "Mr Winehouse is
OL,16,Fclearly a strong character but also
OL,17,Fsomeone who has suffered a great
OL,18,Ftragedy in the loss of his daughter.
OL,26,@sD@ZOUuD@FO]wD@TOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776687067
OL,3,CAmy Winehouse's father loses High
OL,4,CCourt row with singer's friends over
OL,5,Cauctions
OL,7,F"Since Amy's death, he has worked hard
OL,8,Fto keep her memory alive including
OL,9,Fthrough the charitable entity, the Amy
OL,10,FWinehouse Foundation, which supports
OL,11,Fand informs young people through a
OL,12,Fvariety of projects.
OL,14,F"It is also the case that Amy's
OL,15,Festate, including in particular the
OL,16,Froyalties from Back To Black, has made
OL,17,FMr Winehouse personally extremely
OL,18,Fwealthy.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776687067
OL,3,CAmy Winehouse's father loses High
OL,4,CCourt row with singer's friends over
OL,5,Cauctions
OL,7,F"Mr Winehouse is therefore
OL,8,Funderstandably sensitive about anyone
OL,9,Fwho he perceives as exploiting Amy's
OL,10,Fmemory, particularly for financial
OL,11,Fgain, and he is keen to promote the
OL,12,FAWF, but also, in my judgment, he is
OL,13,Fequally sensitive about ensuring that
OL,14,Fthe family continue to benefit
OL,15,Ffinancially."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776687067
OL,3,CAmy Winehouse's father loses High
OL,4,CCourt row with singer's friends over
OL,5,Cauctions
OL,7,FShe also said that Mr Winehouse "likes
OL,8,Fto dominate people and situations",
OL,9,Fthat she found him to be an
OL,10,F"unreliable witness" and that he
OL,11,Fbrought the claim "without bothering
OL,12,Fto check until shortly before trial"
OL,13,Fthat he had a valid claim for the
OL,14,Fitems he was claiming for.
OL,16,FFollowing the judgment, Ms Parry said:
OL,17,F"Today, the High Court has cleared my
OL,18,Fname, unequivocally and in full, after
OL,19,Fyears of deeply damaging and unfounded
OL,20,Fallegations brought by Mitch Winehouse.
OL,26,@oD@aOUpD@bO]rD@AOUrD@TO]sD@SOUtD@dO]yD@
OL,26,AAOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776687067
OL,3,CAmy Winehouse's father loses High
OL,4,CCourt row with singer's friends over
OL,5,Cauctions
OL,7,F"This was not a partial outcome or a
OL,8,Fmatter of nuance. The claim has failed
OL,9,Fentirely. It should never have been
OL,10,Fbrought.
OL,12,F"I stood beside Amy as a friend, a
OL,13,Fcreative partner, and her costume
OL,14,Fdesigner. What we shared was built on
OL,15,Ftrust, loyalty, and a genuine love of
OL,16,Fthe work.
OL,18,F"To see that relationship
OL,19,Fmisrepresented so publicly has been
OL,20,Fboth painful and profoundly unjust.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                G10/12
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,402,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F401A1776687067
OL,3,CAmy Winehouse's father loses High
OL,4,CCourt row with singer's friends over
OL,5,Cauctions
OL,7,F"This judgment restores the truth. It
OL,8,Fdoes not, however, erase the toll, on
OL,9,Fmy health, my work, and my life, of
OL,10,Fdefending myself against claims that
OL,11,Fhad no evidential foundation."
